## 3. ADVISOR RECRUITMENT TIMELINE

| Week | Action |
|------|--------|
| 1-2 | Draft advisor wish list (10-15 target profiles from LinkedIn) |
| 2-3 | Send outreach messages (personalised, reference Trip Tailors' traction) |
| 3-4 | Initial calls with interested candidates (20 min each) |
| 4-5 | Select top 2-3 candidates. Share business plan for deeper review. |
| 5-6 | Second call: discuss advisory terms, expectations, equity |
| 6-7 | Send advisory agreement for review |
| 7-8 | Sign agreements. First formal advisory call. |
| 8+ | Monthly cadence established. Advisors included in investor materials. |

**Target: 2-3 advisors signed within 8 weeks of starting outreach.**

